Note:
Runa Scientific Computing: Linear Algebra Core (Compatibility Layer)

This is a compatibility wrapper that imports from the unified math linear algebra engine.
All functionality has been moved to math/engine/linalg for better architecture.
:End Note

Import "math/engine/linalg/core" as LinAlgEngine

Note: Re-export all types and functions from the engine
Type DecompositionResult is LinAlgEngine.DecompositionResult
Type LinearSystemResult is LinAlgEngine.LinearSystemResult
Type SolverMethod is LinAlgEngine.SolverMethod
Type MatrixNorm is LinAlgEngine.MatrixNorm

Note: Re-export matrix operations
Process called "matrix_multiply" that takes a as Any and b as Any returns Any:
    Return LinAlgEngine.matrix_multiply with a as a and b as b

Process called "matrix_transpose" that takes matrix as Any returns Any:
    Return LinAlgEngine.matrix_transpose with matrix as matrix

Process called "matrix_inverse" that takes matrix as Any returns Any:
    Return LinAlgEngine.matrix_inverse with matrix as matrix

Process called "matrix_determinant" that takes matrix as Any returns Float:
    Return LinAlgEngine.matrix_determinant with matrix as matrix

Process called "matrix_rank" that takes matrix as Any returns Integer:
    Return LinAlgEngine.matrix_rank with matrix as matrix

Process called "matrix_trace" that takes matrix as Any returns Float:
    Return LinAlgEngine.matrix_trace with matrix as matrix

Note: Re-export decomposition functions
Process called "lu_decomposition" that takes matrix as Any returns DecompositionResult:
    Return LinAlgEngine.lu_decomposition with matrix as matrix

Process called "qr_decomposition" that takes matrix as Any returns DecompositionResult:
    Return LinAlgEngine.qr_decomposition with matrix as matrix

Process called "cholesky_decomposition" that takes matrix as Any returns DecompositionResult:
    Return LinAlgEngine.cholesky_decomposition with matrix as matrix

Process called "svd" that takes matrix as Any returns DecompositionResult:
    Return LinAlgEngine.svd with matrix as matrix

Process called "eigendecomposition" that takes matrix as Any returns DecompositionResult:
    Return LinAlgEngine.eigendecomposition with matrix as matrix

Note: Re-export solver functions
Process called "solve_linear_system" that takes a as Any and b as Any returns LinearSystemResult:
    Return LinAlgEngine.solve_linear_system with a as a and b as b

Process called "solve_least_squares" that takes a as Any and b as Any returns LinearSystemResult:
    Return LinAlgEngine.solve_least_squares with a as a and b as b

Note: Re-export norm functions
Process called "matrix_norm" that takes matrix as Any and norm_type as Any returns Float:
    Return LinAlgEngine.matrix_norm with matrix as matrix and norm_type as norm_type

Process called "vector_norm" that takes vector as Any and norm_type as Any returns Float:
    Return LinAlgEngine.vector_norm with vector as vector and norm_type as norm_type

Process called "condition_number" that takes matrix as Any returns Float:
    Return LinAlgEngine.condition_number with matrix as matrix